msgctxt "164_Matsuyama"
msgid "That was just sublime! Great fish, great rice... Simply beautiful!"
msgstr "¡Eso fue sublime! Pescado delicioso, un gran arroz... ¡Simplemente hermoso!"

msgctxt "176_Kiryu"
msgid "It was good... but did you get any ideas?"
msgstr "Era bueno pero... ¿has tienes alguna idea?"

msgctxt "188_Matsuyama"
msgid "Not really."
msgstr "En realidad, no."

msgctxt "200_Kiryu"
msgid "Nothing? Oh, well. We might as well take our time. Let's go somewhere else."
msgstr "¿Nada? Oh, bueno. Deberíamos tomarnos nuestro tiempo. Vayamos a otro sitio."

msgctxt "224_Matsuyama"
msgid "Where to next?"
msgstr "¿Adónde vamos ahora?"

msgctxt "236_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's go eat some tasty yakiniku. I think it has something in common with that rich tonkotsu ramen at Kyushu No. 1 Star. "
msgstr "Vamos a comer un buen yakiniku. Creo que tiene algo en común con ese delicioso ramen tonkotsu de Kyushu No. 1 Star. "

msgctxt "248_Matsuyama"
msgid "Great idea! Let's go! "
msgstr "¡Qué buena idea! ¡Vamos! "

msgctxt "272_Kiryu"
msgid "Let's go eat some top-notch sushi."
msgstr "Vamos a comer sushi de primera."

msgctxt "284_Matsuyama"
msgid "Got it. Expensive, high-end seafood would be the exact opposite of the affordable, hearty tonkotsu ramen we serve. "
msgstr "Entendido. Mariscos caros y de alta gama serían todo lo contrario de nuestro ramen tonkotsu accesible y sustancioso. "

msgctxt "296_Kiryu"
msgid "Exactly. Let's go. "
msgstr "Exacto. Vamos. "

msgctxt "308_Matsuyama"
msgid "You're the boss! "
msgstr "¡Tú mandas! "

msgctxt "332_Kiryu"
msgid "Ramen's all about serving good food fast and cheap. With that in mind, it might be worthwhile to visit a fast food joint. "
msgstr "El ramen se trata de servir buena comida rápido y barata. Con eso en mente, podría valer la pena visitar un local de comida rápida. "

msgctxt "344_Matsuyama"
msgid "Great idea! I never thought of that! "
msgstr "¡Buena idea! ¡Nunca lo había pensado! "

msgctxt "356_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay, let's go to Smile Burger. "
msgstr "Vale, vamos a Smile Burger. "

msgctxt "368_Matsuyama"
msgid "You're the boss! "
msgstr "¡Tú mandas! "

msgctxt "392_Kiryu"
msgid "Maybe we're trying too hard. Let's wander around a little for a change of pace. "
msgstr "Tal vez estamos esforzándonos demasiado. Vamos a dar una vuelta para cambiar un poco de ritmo. "

msgctxt "404_Matsuyama"
msgid "But..."
msgstr "Pero..."

msgctxt "416_Kiryu"
msgid "You shouldn't overthink things. Let's just take it slow. "
msgstr "No deberías darle tantas vueltas. Mejor vamos despacio. "

msgctxt "428_Matsuyama"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

msgctxt "452_Matsuyama"
msgid "Let's get some tasty yakiniku."
msgstr "Vamos a comer un buen yakiniku."

msgctxt "464_Matsuyama"
msgid "Let's see what fast food has to offer."
msgstr "Veamos qué nos ofrece la comida rápida."

msgctxt "476_Matsuyama"
msgid "Let's just wander around town."
msgstr "Demos una vuelta por la ciudad."

